      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring a 7,900 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable differential. To ensure longevity, the rod bearings have been addressed with VAC coated shells, the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with steel plates. The suspension geometry is preserved via refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior reflects its age with minor cosmetic imperfections, the drivetrain performance is optimized for high-lateral-G environments and precision cornering.",
